WEBVTT

00:00:02.898 --> 00:00:05.098
Shah Rukh Khan: Our performer today
decided to follow her dream

00:00:05.098 --> 00:00:06.952
of composing music for films in Mumbai

00:00:06.952 --> 00:00:11.051
and so left her hometown
Indore at the age of 20.

00:00:11.171 --> 00:00:13.331
Today on the basis
of her talent and hard work

00:00:13.331 --> 00:00:15.591
she is not just an award-winning
music composer,

00:00:15.591 --> 00:00:18.261
but also a successful music innovator.

00:00:18.508 --> 00:00:22.198
Today she will transport us
into her special musical zone.

00:00:22.198 --> 00:00:25.007
Please join us in welcoming on
TED Talks India New Thoughts,

00:00:25.007 --> 00:00:29.278
our country's young musical
icon, Sneha Khanwalkar.

00:00:29.326 --> 00:00:32.326
(Music)